    "longDescription": "Bring customer context into the work that moves deals forward. Find high-priority accounts and signals, prepare for customer meetings, complete follow-ups, propose customer-record updates, build close plans, and review deals at risk.\n\nStart with CRM details, call notes, docs, messages, calendar events, uploaded files, or pasted context. Connect tools like Salesforce, HubSpot, Slack, Outreach, Clay, Rox, and Actively to bring scattered account context together and turn the available evidence into practical next steps.",
